{"tid":2396104,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"深圳返港免檢經商確診列本地個案","createTime":"2021-02-05T10:32:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T01:44:54.000Z","uid":5195,"like":7,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"f4fd0c4a45e71dc466f2a098de5fa5f64d57ab28","tid":2396104,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T10:32:12.000Z","msg":"本地個案方面，共有34宗，9宗屬無源頭個案，其中編號10581個案居於深圳，上月23日來港，屬商務豁免人士。該名確診者於上月21日在深圳接受檢測，結果呈陰性，惟上月30號開始出現頭痛等病徵，前日(3日)再進行檢測後證實確診。<br />\n<br />\n張竹君：確診者一半時間在港暫列本地個案<br />\n<br />\n張竹君表示，該名確診者一半時間在港，一半時間在深圳，暫列為本地個案，「因為想做多啲控制措施，但會同深圳溝通，睇下佢哋有無野要做」。該人士在港期間居於東涌映灣園三期悅濤軒9座曾赴東薈城購物，但在港逗留期間並無特別活動。該大廈須納人強制檢測令。她又補充指，該患者整年未有返港，一直逗留內地工作，會與內地繼續了解佢其在內地情況。"},{"pid":"eb1baa55e4190a99bb3ad1a8555542144d555a4a","tid":2396104,"uid":281483,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T10:35:00.000Z","msg":"深圳零確診<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77e0ac6b0196f6282731744ca285a734188322da","tid":2396104,"uid":58630,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T10:37:19.000Z","msg":"點解一半香港一半深圳就計香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd65aab55bd56f4d7350ad4ae9b6425eddd97c7c","tid":2396104,"uid":13663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T10:39:35.000Z","msg":"唔驗咪零囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那人仲危險"},{"pid":"694b1aa52ceee0e23657c4f51ab4f5dd356e4762","tid":2396104,"uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"77e0ac6b0196f6282731744ca285a734188322da","tid":2396104,"uid":58630,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T10:37:19.000Z","msg":"點解一半香港一半深圳就計香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T10:39:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lick.gif\" cla